description: Collects : X-Men (1991) #112 - Uncanny X-Men (1981) # 392 - X-Men Unlimited (1993) #31 "Gold" - X-Men Unlimited (1993) #32 "Beyond The Music"
name: Nuova Serie n.15 : L'alba della distribuzione 2 di 3

description:
It's more fun with Fractals as the Squaddies are imbued with the power of overweightedness; costume up as the classic Marvel Monsters for a spooky party down Memory Lane; come together to protect a small village from the diabolical desperado, El Doom, in a tale out of time in the Old West; and pitch in to make sure Christmas goes off without a hitch when Santa and his Reindeer have a little fender-bender with the Helicarrier!

Plus: Tigra, She-Hulk, and The Wasp join the team - and the Super Hero Squad will never be the same! Also featuring a tour of the S.H.I.E.L.D. Helicarrier with the Falcon; a camping trip with Wolverine, Reptil and Falcon; a Halloween Party at the Baxter Building; and more!

Collecting SUPER HERO SQUAD #8-12.
name: Super Hero Squad: A Squad For All Seasons

volume.name: Super Hero Squad: A Squad For All Seasons

description: Collects : X-Men (1991) #113 -  Uncanny X-Men (1981) # 393  - X-Men Unlimited (1993) #31 "Monsters" -  X-Men Unlimited (1993) #32 "All's Swell That Ends Swell?!"
name: Nuova Serie n.16 : L'alba della distribuzione 3 di 3

description: During his trip to America, Christopher Columbus brought with him, by the will of the Spanish royal family, a mysterious passenger, with an even more mysterious crate. Four hundred years later , the content of that chest is guarded and revered by the Creek Indians , until the arrival of the expedition of Professor Martin Navarro.
name: Il segreto di Cristoforo Colombo

description: The story of how the ambitious warrior Dagayo tried to unleash the fury of the gods to become the lord of Darkwood. And how the friendship forged between Zagor and Tonka defeated Dagayo and his (false) gods.
name: La congiura degli dei
Topolino e il concerto di Natale
Lo strano caso del dottor Paper e di mister Paperyde

description: In bringing food to the dog Botolo, in the park, Dylan meets Marty, an elderly retired man, with whom he establishes a sincere friendship. Meanwhile, a chain of heinous crimes are continuing in London, but nobody seems to care…
name: Marty

description: Mysterious killings appear to have been committed by freaks long buried in their own cemetery, and from which their bodies have disappeared. Dylan, hired by the sweet Amelia, investigates.
name: Il cimitero dei freaks

description: A lost and unknown inn, in which Dylan is imprisoned against his will, where no one has ever escaped , where everybody is hiding something . An inn at the end of the world .
name: La locanda alla fine del mondo
Zio Paperone e il segreto di Agatha Paperye

description: A killer does not want Sally to be happy and kill all the people in her life.
name: Tutti gli amori di Sally
Zio Paperone e la villa stregata
Zio Paperone e le favolose miniere sottomarine
Zio Paperone e la somiglianza incredibile
Zio Paperone e il furto della torre Eiffel

description: Do guns have a soul? Can they decide who to kill and when? This is what Dylan asks to himself, while investigating on a cursed gun that leads its owners to suicide.
name: Anima d'acciaio
Paperinik e la sparizione di Papery Moon
Zio Paperone e il motore a... pera

description: Due to the recent death of his mother, Merian, Dylan's girlfriend, is forced to confront her past and his deeper anxieties. Following the disappearance of his father at an early age she developed a strong phobia towards the earth and all that it can grow, but his mother's funeral in her old country will provide an opportunity to finally win the old trauma. And Dylan will be forced to deal with these memories together with Merian, following with her the road through the "living forest" that leads the "field of the dead" and what it contains: the truth.
name: I ricordi sepolti
Zio Paperone e i rottami spaziali

description: Dylan, mysteriously called to court on day 6-6, sixth class, 66th floor, finds himself torn between different scenarios and nightmarish reality and dream. Is the world to be gone mad or is the nightmare investigator?
name: Ascensore per l'inferno

description: The Phantasm series revolves around The Tall Man, an evil monster who is out to get Reggie a young man who is trying to defeat him once and for all.
name: Phantasm #1

description: Martin is in Italy for an episode of "The Mysteries of Mystery" and is "invited" by Aaron to take care of a Mystery that links the island of Pianosa to Caravaggio. A reluctant Martin, therefore, falls into a dangerous investigation about the murder of a researcher, crosses the tracks of the Knights Templar and the Knights of Malta to reach almost to the discovery of an artifact that could change the fate of Christian civilization.
name: Il codice Caravaggio

description: Martin is involuntarily involved in a conspiracy of vast proportions. Fortunately for him, a young hacker who is considered died is in fact still "online" and helps him to unravel the tangled skein.
name: Emoticon :-(

description: An episode of Martin’s transmission dedicated to Amelia Earhart brings the detective in the middle of a shameful and horrible mystery involving Japan, the United States and China. While the lives of Diana and Java are in danger, Martin must find the antidote to a mysterious epidemic that has hit a Chinese village, theater years before of the atrocities of the notorious "Unit 731".
name: L'ultimo viaggio di Amelia Earhart

description: Martin Mystere answers the call of a former opponent and runs into one of the most bizarre mysteries of his career . What binds a fantastic tale of an old popular journal to the legends related to a sea branch of Nova Scotia , Canada ? And what to do with the legends of the " Pit of Oak Island " that Martin already visited during one of his adventures ?
name: Il tesoro di Capitan Kidd

description: Looking for informations about the tradition of the “Black Man", Martin, along with Java, goes to Cape Rock,New England, along with two ”Altrove” agents and a former one.The group have to face a dangerous ghost that keeps cruelly captive the souls of the deads of the town.
name: L'orrore di Cape Rock

description: A fan of illusionists comes at 3 Washington Mews , claiming to be aware of the most amazing secret of Harry Houdini . This is the diary of a dark magician of the eighteenth century, which would affect the career of the legendary " Escape Artist " . Through reading the diary, Martin Mystere is involved in a series of events initiated in France during the fourteenth century, and find its climax today , in the well- known basis of " Elsewhere ."
name: Il grande Houdini

description: The buyers of a perfect and beautiful mechanical chinese peacock die in mysterious circumstances. Accused of a crime is one of the former "protected" by Diana, who, with the help of Martin tries to unravel the mystery and clear his position.
name: Il pavone dell'Imperatore

description:
Overview

TWO CAPTAIN AMERICAS LEAD A TIME-TRAVELING PATRIOTIC SQUAD TO RESTORE LIBERTY! Steve Rogers and Jim Barnes – joined by US Agent, American Dream and Commander A -- now they find themselves in a dystopic America -- and branded as traitors. Can they survive in a nation that has surrendered its soul to the mysterious AMERICOMMAND? Roger Stern (CAPTAIN AMERICA: WAR & REMEMBRANCE) and Philippe Briones (IRON MAN: LEGACY) will show you a world where the Captains America have been declared ENEMIES OF THE STATE!
name: Enemies of the State

description:
Meno di Zero [Less than Zero]

The first Italian Super-Team is ready to enter in action, but they need the approval of the Euromind, European Division of S.H.E.L.D., and Agent Lancelot have the job of test them. How? Holographic Danger Room set up with Avengers Symulation!

Demoni del Passato [Demon of the Past]

The Eurolab, the scientific team of the Euromind, is investigating on some strange cave-system found in an archeological site in Spain. When horrible monster and ancient secret of the spainish inquisition start to menace the scientist, the Task Force, the military arm of the Eurolab, open fire...
name: Meno di Zero / Demoni Del Passato

description:
The first story - "Captain America" - about talk aunt May with Steven Rogers.

The second - "Thor" - about life after death.

The third - "Rogue" - about this ex X-man and her feeling about the death of friends.
name: Chapter Two of Six

description: Collects : Uncanny X-Men (1981) # 400 - Rogue (2001) #03 -  X-Men Unlimited (1993) #33 "Special Attraction"
name: Nuova Serie n.21
